EEDS TO BE CITED-->\n* '''Al-Zohour''' District:<!-- {{convert|262,581|km2|sqmi|abbr=on}}-->\n* '''Al-Dawahy''' District:<!-- {{convert|62,673|km2|sqmi|abbr=on}}-->\n* '''Al-Sharq''' District:<!-- {{convert|5,017|km2|sqmi|abbr=on}}-->\n* '''Al-Manakh''' District:<!-- {{convert|3,312|km2|sqmi|abbr=on}}-->\n* '''Al-Arab''' District:<!-- {{convert|1,592|km2|sqmi|abbr=on}}-->\n* '''Gharb''' District:\n\nThere is also [[Port Fuad]] city <!--({{convert|505,695|km2|sqmi|disp=s|abbr=on}})--> under the jurisdiction of the [[Port Said Governorate]] forming [[Metropolitan area|metropolitan]] Port Said.\n\n===Squares===\n* Mansheya Square, in Al-Sharq district\n* Al-Shohda Square, in Al-Sharq district\n* AL-Mohafza Square (The governorate Square), in Al-Sharq district\n* AL-Sayed Metwaly Square (formerly ''Al-Estad Square''), in Al-Manakh district\n* [[Volgograd]] Square, in Al-Manakh district\n* [[Bizerte]] Square, in Al-Zohour district\n* Haye Al-Zohour Square, in Al-Zohour district\n* AL-Horeya garden Square, in [[Port Fouad]] city\n\n===Recreational===\n* Ferial Garden\n* The History Garden\n* Montaza Gardens\n* Al-Amal Garden\n* Al-Farama Garden\n* AL-Horeya Garden\n* [[Saad Zaghloul|Saad Zaghlul]] Garden\n* Restaurants Complex\n\n==Port Said city image gallery==\n<center>\n<gallery>\nFile:PortSaidEgypt2 byDanielCsorfoly.JPG|Port Said coastline\nFile:A unique house of Port Said.JPG|The unique type of houses in Port Said making use of [[arch]]es\nFile:Port said eglise cophete.jpg|Port Said (postcard around 1915)\nFile:Port Said.jpg|Modern Port Said at night\nFile:Port Said Suez Canal.jpg|Tourist jetty in Port Said\nFile:Port Said, Monument of Lesseps (n.d.) - front - TIMEA.jpg|Monument of Lesseps\nFile:Port Said - panoramio.jpg|Mosque in Port Said\nFile:Egypt-IMG 0960.jpg|Old lighthouse of Port Said\nFile:PORT-SA\u00cfD. BUREAUX DE LA COMPAGNIE DU CANAL DE SUEZ (n.d.) - front - TIMEA.jpg|Building of Suez Canal Authority in Port Said \nFile:PORT SAID. RUE DU COMMERCE. (n.d.)